About Rentify
Rentify aims to make renting easier, more accessible, and hassle-free. Whether you're looking for a cozy apartment, a spacious house, or a commercial property, Rentify helps you find the ideal place that fits your needs and budget. Our user-friendly interface and comprehensive property listings make it simple to explore various options and connect with property owners directly.

For property owners, Rentify offers an effective platform to showcase your properties to a wide audience. With our easy-to-use listing tools, you can quickly add your property details, upload photos, and reach potential tenants without any hassle.

Features
User Authentication: Secure login and signup for users.
Property Listings: Browse through various property listings and find your ideal rental.
Add Listing: Property owners can add their listings easily.
Responsive Design: Optimized for both desktop and mobile devices.
Getting Started
To get a local copy up and running follow these simple steps.

Prerequisites
Ensure you have the following installed:

Node.js
npm (Node Package Manager)
Installation
Clone the repo:

sh
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/tejasva28/rentify.git
Navigate to the project directory:

sh
Copy code
cd rentify
Install NPM packages:

sh
Copy code
npm install
Start the development server:

sh
Copy code
npm start
